If you have problems trying to mount it with daemon tool here another way to mount it.

1. Unrar with winrar or whatever you have. (h-psts.part001) Unrar that file. doesn't matter.

2. When fnish unrar, you should see a disc (photoshop topsecret.) GRAB and DRAG the disc file onto your desktop.

3. check desktop to see if file is there. Than mount image with daemon tool by going to desktop and you should see the file.

4.After mounting you should see a yellow file saying open folder to view file. click on it.

5. you see "start here" along with "data" and "project file" Click on "start here" than it should work when it opens with firefox or internet explorer.
